content: @Lucas Prieels your error code implies you have a few things wrong in your build setup

Wrote a long detailed response, but I suspect you're running into a problem trying to add a file is merely different by an extension. There could be other things going on, but you're only giving me half the picture by posting files you've added. You need to run "svn diff > mychanges.patch" to capture all the changes you've made elsewhere too so I can see what you've changed. You should read that patch file too. ;)
